| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0393 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9eb4ec1f-b518-5bf1-8de2-a54f8a95fd59"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
